name: Zig Zag Vaulted Box S-L
description: The Zig Zag Vaulted Box adds a fun pop as an accent piece. Available in Small & Large. Handmade; Shagreen/Pen Shell & Bronze-Patina Brass, wood veneer interior. Wipe clean with soft dry cloth. Made in Philippines. All shagreen-covered items should be kept out of direct sunlight; color variants may occur on the stingray and other exotic finishes, but this showcases the Parisian label's commitment to creating authentic luxurious products using natural components.
